sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Knative as Knative Activator/Queue<br/>mTLS (Istio)
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>(transformer-container)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP | 8085/TCP gRPC
    participant TGIS as TGIS Container<br/>(kserve-container)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant GPU as GPU / Model
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(user-workload-monitoring)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ (SIMPLE)
    Gateway->>Knative: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS (Istio)
    Knative->>Caikit: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (Istio)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC localhost:8033<br/>plaintext
    TGIS->>GPU: Model inference<br/>in-process
    GPU-->>TGIS: Prediction result
    TGIS-->>Caikit: gRPC response
    Caikit-->>Knative: HTTP response
    Knative-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response (TLS)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC call (caikit.runtime.Nlp)<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443 TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>Knative: gRPC/HTTP2<br/>8085/TCP mTLS
    Knative->>Caikit: gRPC/HTTP2 (h2c)<br/>8085/TCP mTLS
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC localhost:8033<br/>plaintext
    TGIS-->>Caikit: gRPC response
    Caikit-->>Knative: gRPC response (mTLS)
    Knative-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response (TLS)

    Note over S3,TGIS: Flow 3: Model Loading (Startup)
    S3-->>Caikit: KServe Storage Initializer<br/>downloads to /mnt/models/<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS credentials
    Note over TGIS: TGIS loads model from<br/>/mnt/models/artifacts/
    Note over Caikit: Caikit lazy-loads model<br/>metadata from /mnt/models/

    Note over Prometheus,Caikit: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086 PERMISSIVE mTLS
    Caikit-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
